    "name": "FiloraFS-Lite",
    "description": "# 📂 FiloraFS-Lite API Collection — BuildBaseKit\n\nThis collection showcases a **lightweight file management system** built with Spring Boot.  \nDesigned for developers who want a clean, production-ready way to handle file uploads, storage, and retrieval without building everything from scratch.\n\n---\n\n## ⚡ What’s Included\n\n- File Upload (UUID-based naming)\n    \n- File Streaming (images, videos, downloads)\n    \n- File Deletion\n    \n- File Listing\n    \n- File Metadata (size, type, timestamps)\n    \n\n---\n\n## 🚀 Quick Flow\n\nUpload file → `/file`  \nGet filename (UUID returned)  \nAccess file → `/file/{filename}`  \nView all files → `/file/list`  \nGet file info → `/file/info/{filename}`  \nDelete file → `/file/{filename}`\n\n---\n\n## 🔑 Setup\n\nSet `base_url` → `http://localhost:8000`  \nAdd header → `X-API-KEY:`\n\n---\n\n## 🌐 BuildBaseKit\n\nThis collection is part of BuildBaseKit — production-ready backend boilerplates.  \n👉 [https://buildbasekit.com](https://buildbasekit.com/)\n\n---\n\nRun requests in sequence for best experience.",
